{"id": "ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4", "rating": 4, "userRatingCount": 25, "displayName": {"text": "Rice Dynasty", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNMVNqRkZhSFJ4VEV4MU9VZG5jbWhZZW5oaGVIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My favorite spot near campus. Everything is so good food, service, all of it.\nHighly recommend the beef tomato lotus leaf rice, it has this super subtle lotus fragrance that makes it stand out.\nHonestly you can’t go wrong with anything on the menu. 10/10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My favorite spot near campus. Everything is so good food, service, all of it.\nHighly recommend the beef tomato lotus leaf rice, it has this super subtle lotus fragrance that makes it stand out.\nHonestly you can’t go wrong with anything on the menu. 10/10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chee L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109296965082178851291/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6FGsDrIpmc_GxrF-pUO7Ai2IkfU6JbjRn9_aHt2JTm-vyigY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T03:30:47.027466990Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNMVNqRkZhSFJ4VEV4MU9VZG5jbWhZZW5oaGVIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tNMVNqRkZhSFJ4VEV4MU9VZG5jbWhZZW5oaGVIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857d0017f0b47b:0x6e165b2476aeef6e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSWVsQmlibmQ0Ukd0Q00wcGxWRnBTY1V4TVJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Giving 4 stars for the food as it was actually quite tasty. Sadly, the service was a bit of a letdown. Between the long wait and the server asking us to box our food before we were done, we felt unwelcome and rushed. Hopefully, they can improve the pacing and hospitality", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Giving 4 stars for the food as it was actually quite tasty. Sadly, the service was a bit of a letdown. Between the long wait and the server asking us to box our food before we were done, we felt unwelcome and rushed. Hopefully, they can improve the pacing and hospitality", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michael Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111541299734080395898/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyEf_6JlNFVFka3Mt6luAxGc-EGkrXDa1Kw7lF1Dk944jrhQA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-04T05:38:58.717381956Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSWVsQmlibmQ0Ukd0Q00wcGxWRnBTY1V4TVJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSWVsQmlibmQ0Ukd0Q00wcGxWRnBTY1V4TVJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857d0017f0b47b:0x6e165b2476aeef6e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCelNHRkRTbTlwTlcxNllrVk5jMEZPZG5BeFluYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I came in late on a Friday afternoon and the place was almost deserted, which is a real shame. The food was delicious and the service was very attentive. I was offered complimentary soup when I came in. When I told them I was vegetarian they offered complimentary steamed veg instead.\nthe 5-mushroom rice is great value for the price. very savory and flavorful, generous portion, delicious with the house sauce. It’s pretty delicate in flavor— I think theres a bit of anise or 5 spice? so delicious when it soaks into the rice. and i have enough to take home for later\nrice bowl and soda was about 20 after tax, before tip", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came in late on a Friday afternoon and the place was almost deserted, which is a real shame. The food was delicious and the service was very attentive. I was offered complimentary soup when I came in. When I told them I was vegetarian they offered complimentary steamed veg instead.\nthe 5-mushroom rice is great value for the price. very savory and flavorful, generous portion, delicious with the house sauce. It’s pretty delicate in flavor— I think theres a bit of anise or 5 spice? so delicious when it soaks into the rice. and i have enough to take home for later\nrice bowl and soda was about 20 after tax, before tip", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Emily Jones", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112841758103378040219/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9j7wEaxCtElcvm-EvfrTg6gfMpw0y9iymMqBcU8F6oILhgA0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-10T22:34:40.976625367Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCelNHRkRTbTlwTlcxNllrVk5jMEZPZG5BeFluYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCelNHRkRTbTlwTlcxNllrVk5jMEZPZG5BeFluYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857d0017f0b47b:0x6e165b2476aeef6e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WalVVODNaMFkyZUhkb2IxRTRXVlpuV2pSUGNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Rice Dynasty has basically become my \"cafeteria\" -- I come here almost every day or every other day. The dishes in the photo are currently my favorites: 姜葱鸡 the Heritage Ginger-Scallion Chicken (Half) and the 叉烧Dynasty Char Siu (Portion).\n\nSince I'm not really a rice person, lately I've been ordering the 姜葱鸡Heritage Ginger-Scallion Chicken (Half) almost every time I come. It comes with free rice and sauce, a side of vegetables, and the daily soup -- which is actually just the right amount of food for me and my roommate. Today was my first time trying the 叉烧 Dynasty Char Siu (Portion), and it was absolutely delicious!\n\nEven though I'm not really a rice person, I was curious when I first started coming here, so I ended up trying almost all of their lotus leaf rice dishes.  My favorites is the Minced Beef with Tomato 免治牛肉蕃茄. Another thing I noticed is that some of the lotus leaf rice dishes feel a bit dry to me, since there is quite a lot of rice. I personally like the Minced Beef with Tomato 免治牛肉蕃茄 more because it has more sauce, so the rice feels less dry.\n\nI know Rice Dynasty is still very new, and I'm excited to see more new menu items in the future. now Rice Dynasty mainly specializes in lotus leaf rice dishes, but for people who don't really eat rice that much -- including me -- I'd love to see more non-rice dishes or new menu items in the future.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Rice Dynasty has basically become my \"cafeteria\" -- I come here almost every day or every other day. The dishes in the photo are currently my favorites: 姜葱鸡 the Heritage Ginger-Scallion Chicken (Half) and the 叉烧Dynasty Char Siu (Portion).\n\nSince I'm not really a rice person, lately I've been ordering the 姜葱鸡Heritage Ginger-Scallion Chicken (Half) almost every time I come. It comes with free rice and sauce, a side of vegetables, and the daily soup -- which is actually just the right amount of food for me and my roommate. Today was my first time trying the 叉烧 Dynasty Char Siu (Portion), and it was absolutely delicious!\n\nEven though I'm not really a rice person, I was curious when I first started coming here, so I ended up trying almost all of their lotus leaf rice dishes.  My favorites is the Minced Beef with Tomato 免治牛肉蕃茄. Another thing I noticed is that some of the lotus leaf rice dishes feel a bit dry to me, since there is quite a lot of rice. I personally like the Minced Beef with Tomato 免治牛肉蕃茄 more because it has more sauce, so the rice feels less dry.\n\nI know Rice Dynasty is still very new, and I'm excited to see more new menu items in the future. now Rice Dynasty mainly specializes in lotus leaf rice dishes, but for people who don't really eat rice that much -- including me -- I'd love to see more non-rice dishes or new menu items in the future.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kaylee W.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100392958625180461039/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7Np5wYHKAoR2uItBfO5ekqNQiwdD-ZHEydKaixP52-z29KnQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T23:25:09.126601778Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WalVVODNaMFkyZUhkb2IxRTRXVlpuV2pSUGNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WalVVODNaMFkyZUhkb2IxRTRXVlpuV2pSUGNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d0017f0b47b:0x6e165b2476aeef6e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe7TwFwB9hYARbu-udiRbFm4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RlNuTXpTRnAwUlRsMldVRjROa28zYTJGTlZXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "The serving size is nice, the food quality is okay. The food taste is not that good however. Not a lot of flavor to be fair. Don’t think it’s worth it but we ball 🙏", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The serving size is nice, the food quality is okay. The food taste is not that good however. Not a lot of flavor to be fair. Don’t think it’s worth it but we ball 🙏", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Abdulhadi Altahan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101308801684947263852/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNa4RMaRb6wT44s3S4HW8HokcOvvjVFifu9mIKq1sN7nVzEas=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T21:57:55.745563426Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/cont